  "remarks": "Ruslan Ostashko is a figure active in the Russian public space. He works as a journalist and TV host on state TV Channel One and is the lead singer of the patriotic music band “Ours”. He is also editor-in-chief of the website “politrussia.com”, a website used to promote the Russian Government’s narrative, including on Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
